<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>Fee Structure | SVIC Inter College</title>
    
    <!-- Font Awesome 6 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
    
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef9f0 0%, #fff4e8 100%);
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ========== TOP HEADER ========== */
        .top-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #060241, #050347, #021853);
            color: #fef9c3;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            font-size: 12px;
            gap: 12px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f59e0b;
        }

        .web-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .web-text p, .web-text a {
            color: #fef9c3;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 11px;
        }

        .highlight-link {
            color: #fcd34d;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .highlight-link:hover {
            color: #f59e0b;
            transform: translateX(3px);
        }

        .right-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .right-text .link {
            color: #fcd34d;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 11px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .right-text .link:hover {
            color: #fff;
            background: rgba(245,158,11,0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* ========== MAIN NAVBAR ========== */
        .main-header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            position: relative;
        }

        .navbar-line {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b, #ec4899, #8b5cf6, #06b6d4, #f59e0b);
            background-size: 200% 100%;
            animation: lineMove 3s ease infinite;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        @keyframes lineMove {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }

        .nav {
            max-width: 1320px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .logo {
            flex-shrink: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .logo img {
            height: 65px;
            width: auto;
            max-width: 220px;
            object-fit: contain;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .logo img { height: 50px; max-width: 180px; }
        }

        .menu {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .upperNav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .nav-button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ec4899, #8b5cf6);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 28px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(245,158,11,0.35);
        }

        .nav-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(236,72,153,0.45);
        }

        .btn-box { display: flex; gap: 12px; }

        .toggle-btn {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 22px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: white;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .toggle-btn:last-child {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #11998e, #38ef7d);
        }

        .toggle-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }

        .lowerNav {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: flex-end;
        }

        .menu-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding: 8px 18px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            color: #1f2937;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .menu-link::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 0%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(120deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
            border-radius: 40px;
            transition: 0.3s;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .menu-link:hover::before { width: 100%; }
        .menu-link:hover { color: #d97706; transform: translateY(-2px); }

        .hamburger {
            display: none;
            flex-direction: column;
            cursor: pointer;
            gap: 5px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .hamburger span {
            width: 28px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f59e0b, #ec4899);
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .menu { display: none; }
            .hamburger { display: flex; }
            .top-header { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
        }

        /* Mobile Menu */
        .mobile-menu-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: -100%;
            width: 85%;
            max-width: 350px;
            height: 100vh;
            background: white;
            z-index: 2000;
            transition: right 0.3s;
            padding: 80px 25px 30px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        .mobile-menu-overlay.active { right: 0; }
        .close-menu {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: #f59e0b;
        }
        .mobile-nav-list { list-style: none; }
        .mobile-nav-list li { margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .mobile-nav-list li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }
        .screen-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            z-index: 1999;
            display: none;
        }
        .screen-overlay.active { display: block; }

        /* ========== FEE STRUCTURE PAGE ========== */
        .page-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b, #2d1b4e, #4c1d95);
            padding: 60px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .page-header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,158,11,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            animation: rotate 20s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .page-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .page-header p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        /* Fee Cards */
        .fee-cards {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .fee-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            position: relative;
        }

        .fee-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .card-header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ec4899);
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            position: relative;
        }

        .card-header i {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .card-header h3 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .card-header .duration {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .card-body {
            padding: 25px;
        }

        .fee-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .fee-row:hover {
            background: #fef3c7;
            padding-left: 10px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .fee-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        .fee-amount {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #f59e0b;
        }

        .total-row {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .total-row .fee-amount {
            color: #ec4899;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* Scholarship Section */
        .scholarship-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7ed, #ffedd5);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b, #ec4899);
            background-clip: text;
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }

        .scholarship-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .scholarship-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .scholarship-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            border-color: #f59e0b;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .scholarship-card i {
            font-size: 45px;
            color: #f59e0b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .scholarship-card h4 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .scholarship-card .discount {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ec4899;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .scholarship-card p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
        }

        /* Payment Options */
        .payment-section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .payment-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .payment-method {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9fafb;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .payment-method:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
        }

        .payment-method i {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #f59e0b;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .payment-method p {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
        }

        /* Fee Note */
        .fee-note {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1b4b, #2d1b4e);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .fee-note i {
            font-size: 40px;
            color: #f59e0b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .fee-note h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .fee-note p {
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e1b4b);
            color: #e0e7ff;
            padding: 40px 20px 20px;
        }

        .footer-container {
            max-width: 1280px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .footer-col h4 {
            color: #f59e0b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .footer-col a, .footer-col p {
            display: block;
            color: #cbd5e6;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-col a:hover { color: #f59e0b; transform: translateX(5px); }

        .footer-bottom {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .page-header h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
            .section-title { font-size: 1.5rem; }
            .fee-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .container { padding: 40px 15px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<%-include('partials/header')%>

<div class="container">
    <!-- Fee Cards for Different Streams -->
    <div class="fee-cards">
        <!-- Science Stream -->
        <div class="fee-card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <i class="fas fa-flask"></i>
                <h3>Science Stream</h3>
                <div class="duration">Class 11th & 12th (PCM/PCB)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i> Admission Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 5,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Tuition Fee (Annual)</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 25,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> Lab & Practical Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 4,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Development Fund</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 3,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i> Miscellaneous</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 2,000</span></div>
                <div class="total-row"><span>Total Annual Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 39,000</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Commerce Stream -->
        <div class="fee-card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
                <h3>Commerce Stream</h3>
                <div class="duration">Class 11th & 12th</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i> Admission Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 5,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Tuition Fee (Annual)</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 22,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-laptop"></i> Computer Lab Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 3,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Development Fund</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 3,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i> Miscellaneous</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 2,000</span></div>
                <div class="total-row"><span>Total Annual Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 35,000</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Arts Stream -->
        <div class="fee-card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <i class="fas fa-palette"></i>
                <h3>Arts Stream</h3>
                <div class="duration">Class 11th & 12th</div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice"></i> Admission Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 4,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Tuition Fee (Annual)</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 18,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Development Fund</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 3,000</span></div>
                <div class="fee-row"><span class="fee-label"><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i> Miscellaneous</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 2,000</span></div>
                <div class="total-row"><span>Total Annual Fee</span><span class="fee-amount">₹ 27,000</span></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scholarship Section -->
    <div class="scholarship-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">🏆 Scholarships & Concessions</h2>
        <div class="scholarship-grid">
            <div class="scholarship-card" onclick="showToast('Merit Scholarship - Up to 50% off on tuition fee')">
                <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                <h4>Merit Scholarship</h4>
                <div class="discount">Up to 50%</div>
                <p>For students scoring 85%+ in previous class</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scholarship-card" onclick="showToast('Sports Quota - Up to 30% fee waiver')">
                <i class="fas fa-futbol"></i>
                <h4>Sports Quota</h4>
                <div class="discount">Up to 30%</div>
                <p>For state/national level sports achievers</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scholarship-card" onclick="showToast('EWS Scholarship - 25% fee concession')">
                <i class="fas fa-hand-holding-heart"></i>
                <h4>EWS Scholarship</h4>
                <div class="discount">25%</div>
                <p>For economically weaker sections (Income &lt; 2.5L)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scholarship-card" onclick="showToast('Defense/Government Employee - 20% concession')">
                <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                <h4>Defense/Government Ward</h4>
                <div class="discount">20%</div>
                <p>For children of defense personnel & govt employees</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scholarship-card" onclick="showToast('Sibling Concession - 15% off')">
                <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                <h4>Sibling Concession</h4>
                <div class="discount">15%</div>
                <p>If two or more siblings studying in SVIC</p>
            </div>
            <div class="scholarship-card" onclick="showToast('Girl Child Scholarship - Special concession')">
                <i class="fas fa-female"></i>
                <h4>Girl Child Scholarship</h4>
                <div class="discount">10%</div>
                <p>Special scholarship for meritorious girl students</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Payment Options -->
    <div class="payment-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">💳 Payment Options</h2>
        <div class="payment-grid">
            <div class="payment-method" onclick="showToast('Online Payment via Net Banking')"><i class="fas fa-university"></i><p>Net Banking</p></div>
            <div class="payment-method" onclick="showToast('Credit/Debit Card Payment')"><i class="fab fa-cc-visa"></i><p>Credit/Debit Card</p></div>
            <div class="payment-method" onclick="showToast('UPI Payment Available')"><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i><p>UPI / QR Code</p></div>
            <div class="payment-method" onclick="showToast('Cash/DD Payment at College Office')"><i class="fas fa-money-bill-wave"></i><p>Cash / Demand Draft</p></div>
            <div class="payment-method" onclick="showToast('EMI Facility Available')"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i><p>EMI Facility (0% Interest)</p></div>
            <div class="payment-method" onclick="showToast('Scholarship Application Available')"><i class="fas fa-gift"></i><p>Scholarship Apply</p></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Important Note -->
    <div class="fee-note">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
        <h3>Important Notes</h3>
        <p>✓ Fees can be paid annually or semester-wise (two installments)<br>
        ✓ 5% discount if full annual fee is paid before 31st March<br>
        ✓ Late fee of ₹200 per month after due date<br>
        ✓ Hostel & Transport facilities available at additional cost<br>
        ✓ Scholarships are subject to verification of documents</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Additional Hostel & Transport Fees -->
    <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <h2 class="section-title">🏠 Additional Facilities (Optional)</h2>
        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 25px;">
            <div style="background: white; border-radius: 20px; padding: 25px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                <i class="fas fa-hotel" style="font-size: 45px; color: #f59e0b; margin-bottom: 15px;"></i>
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px;">Hostel Facility</h3>
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;"><span>Boys Hostel (Annual)</span><span style="color:#ec4899; font-weight:700;">₹ 65,000</span></div>
